The evidence with the title 'The truth about president Obama's skyrocketing spending ' says May 24, 2012  ... What Politifact must have missed is a very important data point : president Obama signed most of the spending attributed to president George W. Bush 's last year in office , which was assigned wrongly to Bush in Nutting's piece. (Heritage's Emily Goff and Alison Fraser set the record straight on The Foundry . ).
